      "chunk_type": "mechanism",
      "source_ref": {"source_doc": "Kuznica Duha v2", "section": "pilot curated card"},
      "core_thesis": "During panic, control often intensifies because the system is trying to restore safety and predictability; answer supportively and avoid diagnostic overclaim.",
